Bobby talks about meeting his girlfriend's parents for the first time at a state park over the weekend! Amy gets emotional at the thought of Bobby becoming a part of their family. We draft our favorite sounds. VOTE for your favorite team at www.BobbyBones.com. Plus, Raymundo wants to trademark his ‘yeaaaaaaah’ catchphrase!
